<p>I am a Chinese student too,like robaggio.We are classmates.
  In China,if we want to go to college,we have to work very hard at high school.
  I woke up at 5:30 am. ,and we would be studying until 23:00 or later.
There is no good idea to deal with that hard life.Because we want education.In China ,there are  4000000++ students join the clollege entrace exam in my province,but only 17% of them can go to college.So we have to work harder and harder.
  I want some change ,but I have no idea&#8230;</p>

